      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a vehicle that exemplifies consistent maintenance and dependable performance. This unit has been thoroughly inspected to ensure its mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal meet our professional standards. Featuring a clean profile and a well-preserved interior, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the pragmatic professional. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a reliable, high-caliber vehicle at a strategic price point.",
