    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been amazing. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained. Perfect for anyone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have! Come take it for a spin!",
